# HighNote runs with ZERO env vars (local demo mode). Each var upgrades one capability.

# --- Cross-device realtime (Supabase) ---
# With both set, submissions persist to Postgres and stream to the dashboard via
# Supabase Realtime — a phone on cellular can update the projector.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=

# --- Live AI (Anthropic) ---
# With a key, "Refresh insights" and "Generate reply" call claude-haiku-4-5.
# If Supabase is ALSO configured, the app prefers the Edge Function proxy so the
# key stays server-side. With only this var (no Supabase), the browser calls the
# API directly using the CORS header. Without it, coherent seeded output is used.
VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# --- Deployed origin for QR codes ---
# QR codes encode this origin (falls back to window.location.origin).
VITE_PUBLIC_URL=

# --- Google review destination ---
# Where the "Post your review on Google" button goes (same for every rating).
# For a real listing use its writereview link:
#   https://search.google.com/local/writereview?placeid=<REAL_PLACE_ID>
# Left blank, it defaults to a Google Maps search for the demo restaurant (never 404s).
VITE_GOOGLE_REVIEW_URL=
